OL,5,G1100 Couples Come Dine with Me
OL,6,     FIn and around Edinburgh, there are
OL,7,     Fsome hard-to-digest jokes, a cat
OL,8,     Fhair catastrophe and a boy band
OL,9,     Frevelation, as three couples put
OL,10,     Ftheir hosting skills to the
OL,11,     Fultimate test.
OL,12,G1200 Couples Come Dine with Me
OL,13,     FIn Edinburgh, Kenny and Lisa serve
OL,14,     Fup 'restaurant quality' food,
OL,15,     FJulie and Keith's courses are
OL,16,     Fsurprisingly similar, and Kate and
OL,17,     FMike get competitive with their
OL,18,     FTex-Mex menu.
