OL,5,G1300 Couples Come Dine with Me
OL,6,     FIn Kent, West End performers
OL,7,     FMillie and Andy serve
OL,8,     FGreek-Cypriot food, and Sam and
OL,9,     FEmma spray their beef Wellington
OL,10,     Fgold. But can 500-time hosts Alex
OL,11,     Fand Richard show them how it's
OL,12,     Fdone?
OL,13,G1400 Couples Come Dine with Me
OL,14,     FIn Kent, Lisa and Iain celebrate
OL,15,     FIain's Highland roots with
OL,16,     FScottish food and bagpipes.
OL,17,     FThere's a shock revelation on
OL,18,     FHannah and Paul's night. And Ling
OL,19,     Fand Mark serve 'Chinglish'
OL,20,     Fcuisine.
